elements.contents:

Land Rustic with 48420sqm Corte de Sobro Aljezur - electricity, water, easy access
prev
next
48.420m²REF PV-T-559

Sale
Rustic land bordering a water stream, located on the Costa Vicentina, great for agriculture. It has 3 ponds, one of them with around 100x50m, with spring water suitable for bathing (analyses carried out by Int. Sup. Tecnico), flanked by pine trees and plains. Good access. Electricity and water from the company nearby. 3.5 km from Rogil, 5 km from Vale dos Homens Beach and 7 km from Aljezur. Highlight for the panoramic views of sea and mountains. Also indicated for the development of nature tourism projects, distinguished by the enormous variety of birds that can be observed, or as a simple place of leisure and rest.
